---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Why Canvas Prints? - KitchingArt"
  description="Learn about the benefits of giclee canvas art prints. High quality, vibrant colours, and ready to hang."
>
  <section class="canvas-page section">
    <div class="container canvas-content">
      <h1>Why canvas prints?</h1>

      <div class="canvas-body">
        <p>Canvas prints offer a premium way to display art in your home. Here's why I chose giclee canvas printing for my work:</p>

        <h2>Quality</h2>
        <p>Fine quality giclee printed canvas of 340gsm in weight. The texture of the canvas adds depth and dimension to the artwork that you simply don't get with paper prints.</p>

        <h2>Vibrant colours</h2>
        <p>Water-based HP Latex inks produce vibrant, accurate colours with UV protection, ensuring your artwork stays vivid for years to come.</p>

        <h2>Ready to hang</h2>
        <p>Each canvas comes stretched over a wooden frame, ready to hang straight out of the box. No need for additional framing — though you can choose to add a black or white wood frame for an even more polished look.</p>

        <h2>Durability</h2>
        <p>Canvas prints are incredibly durable. They're resistant to moisture, won't crack or fade easily, and are much lighter than glass-framed prints, making them safer and easier to hang.</p>

        <h2>Multiple sizes</h2>
        <p>Available in a range of sizes to suit any wall space, from intimate 50x50cm prints to statement 120x120cm canvases.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .canvas-content {
    max-width: 700px;
  }

  .canvas-content h1 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .canvas-body h2 {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .canvas-body p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
</style>
